
control plane:
	kube-apiserver: front end for the control plane
	etcd: key value store of all cluster data
	kube-scheduler: selects node on which to run pods
	kube-controller-manager: runs controller processes
	cloud-controller-manager: gloud specific logic

node componentes (run on each node):
	kubelet: manage containers on a node
	kube-proxy: maintain network rules on node
	container runtime (eg docker, cri-o, containerd)

addons:
	DNS
	Web UI
	Container Resource Monitoring
	cluster-level logging
	network plugins
